data.description: Property is currently under contract with a kickout clause, but still being shown for backup offers!  Welcome to 141 Wando Reach Road located in Wando Point, a lovely gated waterfront neighborhood on the banks of the Wando River with a community dock!  This Charleston-Single home is in 'like new' condition inside & out.  From the time you pull into the driveway, you are greeted by pristine landscaping and an inviting porch that runs the length of the home with views of the Wando River.  As you step inside from the front porch, you are welcomed by neutral colors and gleaming Brazilian Cherry Hardwood floors (yes, there is no carpet anywhere in this home)!  This home also features an open main living area with 10' ceilings on the main and upper levels, and a very flexible . . . (MORE). . . floor plan with endless possibilities! You will find the spacious great room & dining room located in the "heart" of the home with loads of natural light.  The gourmet kitchen with granite counters & tile backsplash overlooks the great room and in-formal dining.  Don't miss the dry bar area for your morning coffee or afternoon beverage as you enjoy the breeze on your screened porch.  Off the foyer is the study, which could also be used as an additional bedroom.  On the main level of this home, you will also find a full hall bathroom (connected to the study) and a laundry room.  The eye-catching master suite is located upstairs at the back of the home for your privacy and features a luxurious master bath with dual vanities, large jetted tub, substantial tiled shower, and His & Her closets.  There are 2 additional bedrooms and a full hall bathroom with double sinks complete the upstairs.  On the first level on this home, you will find an additional 2 bedrooms and full bathroom, which would make a great Mother-In-Law Suite with complete privacy!  This multipurpose area will complete this floor plan and give the new owner a great potential to make it their own, whatever need that may be!  This pristine home is loaded with many extras, including Cherry hardwood floors throughout, wainscoting, crown molding, extensive woodwork throughout, plantation blinds, loads of storage throughout & under the home, large  garage that will accommodate up to 3 vehicles, two new HVAC units in 2021, tankless water heater, substantial attic storage with spray foam insulation, gutters, and so many deluxe features that we cannot begin to list them all!  Great gated neighborhood with community dock!  This home has a convenient location to schools, shopping, I-526, the Charleston Airport, and just a short drive to Downtown Charleston!  This lovingly maintained property is in move-in ready condition and is waiting for you to call it home today!
